                                    "key" : {"type" : "FixedString", "value" : "AnimationTags"},
                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "<ChristianD> Wyll raises his hand lazily, sends pulse of psionic power to transform the patriars into mindflayers"}
                                 },
                                 {
                                    "key" : {"type" : "FixedString", "value" : "Attitude"},
                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "Default"}
                                 },
                                 {
                                    "key" : {"type" : "FixedString", "value" : "CinematicNodeContext"},
                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "A pause, and Wyll raises his his hand lazily. With a pulse of psionic power, the patriars before him transform into mind flayers, kneeling before.\r\n\r\nIf available, Ravengard goes last and most gruesomely, transforming on 'lesser men'."}
