                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "A pause, and Wyll raises his his hand lazily. With a pulse of psionic power, the patriars before him transform into mind flayers, kneeling before.\r\n\r\nIf available, Ravengard goes last and most gruesomely, transforming on 'lesser men'."}
